### ============================================
### Insurance API — Coleccion de pruebas
### ============================================

### 1. Crear cliente
POST http://localhost:3000/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Daniel Romero",
  "email": "daniel@test.com"
}

### 2. Buscar cliente por id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/customers/7c3aacc7-bb3b-46b4-a590-b260b0db40c6

### STANDARD — AUTO — Esperado: monthlyPremium = 120000
POST http://localhost:3000/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "7c3aacc7-bb3b-46b4-a590-b260b0db40c6",
  "branch": "AUTO",
  "ratingStrategy": "STANDARD"
}

### RISK_BASED — LIFE riskScore=50 — Esperado: 135000
POST http://localhost:3000/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "7c3aacc7-bb3b-46b4-a590-b260b0db40c6",
  "branch": "LIFE",
  "ratingStrategy": "RISK_BASED",
  "riskProfile": { "riskScore": 50 }
}

### LOYALTY — HOME customerSince=2020 — Esperado: 63750
POST http://localhost:3000/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "7c3aacc7-bb3b-46b4-a590-b260b0db40c6",
  "branch": "HOME",
  "ratingStrategy": "LOYALTY",
  "riskProfile": { "customerSince": 2020 }
}

### HEALTH STANDARD — Esperado: copayRate=0.20, waitingPeriodDays=30
POST http://localhost:3000/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "7c3aacc7-bb3b-46b4-a590-b260b0db40c6",
  "branch": "HEALTH",
  "ratingStrategy": "STANDARD"
}

### QUOTED -> ISSUED
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/policies/0f1d1464-d92a-46f7-b208-942fc2fa9dc5/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "targetStatus": "ISSUED" }

### ISSUED -> ACTIVE
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/policies/0f1d1464-d92a-46f7-b208-942fc2fa9dc5/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "targetStatus": "ACTIVE" }

### ACTIVE -> SUSPENDED
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/policies/0f1d1464-d92a-46f7-b208-942fc2fa9dc5/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "targetStatus": "SUSPENDED" }

### SUSPENDED -> ACTIVE (reactivar)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/policies/0f1d1464-d92a-46f7-b208-942fc2fa9dc5/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "targetStatus": "ACTIVE" }

### ACTIVE -> CANCELLED
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/policies/0f1d1464-d92a-46f7-b208-942fc2fa9dc5/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "targetStatus": "CANCELLED" }

### ERROR — CANCELLED -> ACTIVE (400)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/policies/0f1d1464-d92a-46f7-b208-942fc2fa9dc5/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "targetStatus": "ACTIVE" }

### ERROR — LOYALTY sin antiguedad (400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "7c3aacc7-bb3b-46b4-a590-b260b0db40c6",
  "branch": "HOME",
  "ratingStrategy": "LOYALTY",
  "riskProfile": { "customerSince": 2025 }
}

### ERROR — RISK_BASED sin riskScore (400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "7c3aacc7-bb3b-46b4-a590-b260b0db40c6",
  "branch": "AUTO",
  "ratingStrategy": "RISK_BASED"
}

### ERROR — email duplicado (409)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Daniel Romero",
  "email": "daniel@test.com"
}

### ERROR — poliza no encontrada (404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/policies/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Polizas de un cliente
GET http://localhost:3000/api/policies/customer/7c3aacc7-bb3b-46b4-a590-b260b0db40c6
